description:
Owen is a 20 year old southern boy who is in his sophomore year of college in a pre-med program. He is very into taking care of his body and is a very athletic guy.
He says his favorite thing to do outdoors is anything involving water-- surfing & water skiing top the list for him. He's currently single and looking. We have a feeling he won't be looking for long before he finds a girl who'll be all over him. And who'd be able to blame her?.... Owen has a beautiful body and an extra special 'tool' that he proves he knows how to use here in his NDM video. Enjoy watching Owen... we certainly did.
title: Owen
